snippet.title: [Hindi] BMSD 2025 | Grand Finals | Day 2
snippet.description:
The Top 8 teams from the Semi Finals and Top 8 teams from the Survival Stage are set to battle across 3 intense days of high-stakes BGMI action. The competition is fierce, the pressure is real, and only one team will rise above the rest.

The team that finishes at the top of the leaderboard will earn a slot at the global stage, as the journey to go Beyond Limits reaches its peak!

Teams Playing:
OnePlus K9 Esports
Hero Xtreme Godlike
iQOO ORANGUTAN
Team AX
Infinix TrueRippers
OnePlus Gods Reign

Nebula Esports
FS ESPORTS

Victores Sumus
Madkings
mysterious4 Esports
OnePlus Cincinnati Kids
iQOO 8BIT

snippet.title: KRAMP Trailer | Kiran Abbavaraam | Yukti Thareja | Jains Nani | Razesh Danda | Hasya Movies
snippet.description:
KRAMP Trailer on Hasya Movies.

KRAMP is an Upcoming 2025 Telugu Movie Starring Kiran Abbavaraam, Yukti Thareja & Others. Directed by Jains Nani. Music by Chaitan Bharadwaj. Produced by Razesh Danda under Hasya Movies Banner and Shiva Bommak under Ruudransh Celluloid. The film is set to release in theaters this Diwali on October 18, 2025.

snippet.title: Marvel Studios' Wonder Man - Official Teaser Trailer (2026) Yahya Abdul-Mateen II, Ben Kingsley
snippet.description:
Take a look at the 'Casting' Teaser Trailer for Wonder Man, the next action-adventure superhero installment in the MCU distributed by Marvel Studios. Wonder Man is streaming in January 2026 exclusively on Disney+.

Hollywood actor Simon Williams is thrust into the world of superheroes as he gets powers of his own, and becomes the new superhero Wonder Man.

Wonder Man stars Yahya Abdul-Mateen II, Ben Kingsley, Demetrius Grosse, Lauren Glazier, Byron Bowers, and more. The series was created by Destin Daniel Cretton.

Wonder Man is streaming in January 2026 exclusively on Disney+.

#WonderMan #MCU #IGN

snippet.title: Tu Subah Hai - Diwali Full Animation | Free Fire MAX
snippet.description:
When love is true, sacrifice follows. When courage rises, legends are born. This Diwali, let emotions ignite the battlefield.

Experience the emotion. Feel the battle. 

Music: Akshay & IP
Lyrics: IP Singh
Singers: IP Singh, Sudhir Yaduvanshi
Music Arranged & Produced: Hrishikesh Gangan, Akshay Raheja
Guitars: Chaitanya Bhaidkar
Mix & Master: Ashwin Kulkarni

Lyrics: 

Tu subah hai,
ya saba hai,
ya koi ishq ka falsafa hai.
Tu dua hai,
ya sazaa hai,
ya koi taaron ki kehkashan hai.
‚Äã

Saari dildaari teri,
yeh ishqdaari teri,
sudh-budh khoyi maine,
chadhi hai khumaari teri.
Khud se hua alag,
tujhse mila jo mere,
yaara.... yaara...
tujhse mila toh khud ko haara.
‚Äã

Ishq mein tere duniya se kya,
shaitanon se bhi lad jaaun,
bas tujhko hi main paaun.
‚Äã
Ek prem hi hai sach,
baaki sab toh yahaan pe jhootha hai re,
mujhko tujh mein mil jaana re, mil jaana re.‚Äã

Jab tak meri saans chalti,
mera har ik taana-baana tera hai... tera hai...
Roshni hai jab tak teri mere dil mein,
toh zara bhi na andhera hai... andhera hai...

‚ÄãSaans meri ruk jaaye toh bhi,
teri khushboo saath mein hogi.
Lau jali meri aankhon mein,
toh jeet apni preet ki hogi.

‚Äã
Tu subah hai,
ya saba hai,
ya koi ishq ka falsafa hai.

Catch the thrilling Success Trailer for the blockbuster Odia movie CHARDHAM, starring Anubhav Mohanty and Anuradha Panigrahi. It's a massive hit and is Running Successfully in theaters!

Superstar Anubhav Mohanty stars in #CHARDHAM ‚Äì A Journey Within.

"CHARDHAM - A Journey Within" is a major blockbuster, celebrated as one of the most successful Odia films in recent times. It has drawn massive crowds and strong emotional responses from family audiences, setting a new benchmark for the Odia film industry.

snippet.title: Ikrar Ho Na Jaye | Zinda Dil | Alka Yagnik Songs | Abbas | Ashima Bhalla
snippet.description:
Step into the world of resonant romance with Alka Yagnik's enchanting voice in the unforgettable track 'Ikrar Ho Na Jaye' from the movie Zinda Dil. This soulful melody from the early 2000s is sure to rekindle the season of love in your hearts. Let the silky timbre of Alka Yagnik, the queen of romantic numbers, transport you to an era where music was emotionally stirring and purely heartfelt. Dive deep into the pool of nostalgia and let the magic of the song wrap you in its romantic embrace.

Ikrar Ho Na Jaye



Credits :

Song: Ikrar Ho Na Jaye
Album: Zinda Dil
Artist: Alka Yagnik
Music Director: Nadeem-Shravan
Lyricist: Sameer
